=Description=

"Free Game Arts promotes the use and development of free, "open source" game resources, including 3D models, sound effects, textures, games and development tools. To submit your content, choose a license, then tell us where we can download your content in a zip file with a text file explaining which license it uses. Free Game Arts cannot host derivative works such as characters or places from books, movies, etc. unless the original is in the public domain or under a free license."
(http://virtualworlds.wikia.com/wiki/Free_Game_Arts)

